Package com.example.OpenWeatherProject.stats

Class CityStats

java.lang.Object
com.example.OpenWeatherProject.stats.CityStats
Direct Known Subclasses:
JSONStructure
public class CityStats extends Object
This class is used to define all the attributes that characterize the statistics concerning the temperature of a city.
